AUDIENCE: I was wondering, what
would you do differently

00:44:36.695 --> 00:44:39.120
if you redid the project?

00:44:39.120 --> 00:44:40.960
BRIAN SCHIRMER: Ooh, what would
we do differently if we

00:44:40.960 --> 00:44:43.340
redid the project?

00:44:43.340 --> 00:44:44.590
You want to field that?

